Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DIALOGUE
Dialogue: 3,0:00:01.71,0:00:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago, on Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 3,0:00:04.06,0:00:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up on waiting for her to show up,
Dialogue: 3,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was about to go home alone.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:11.84,0:00:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have imagined this\Ncrushing loneliness on my way here.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:20.59,0:00:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I... rejected?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:23.87,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I'll face her at school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:32.11,0:00:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.07,0:00:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:35.05,0:00:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me someone stood you up?!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:43.12,0:00:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give me a ride.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to go pick up a Christmas cake.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:48.38,0:00:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, my mom and I have a Christmas party together.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.61,0:00:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.68,0:00:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come over to my place?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:58.54,0:01:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom and I can't finish the cake with just the two of us.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:01.03,0:01:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have the leftovers.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:04.08,0:01:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just give me a ride to the bakery.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can decide whether you want to come or not on our way there.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:11.42,0:01:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.  Let's go!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!  What a reaction!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, it's you, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just suddenly bite my ear!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it feel good?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't anything special.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:24.85,0:03:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, if you like biting so much, go ahead and bite this ear too.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't {\i1}actually{\i0\fscx140} {\r}bite it!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell me to?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but you don't normally do that!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can, because of the relationship we have.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:42.66,0:03:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, because we're strangers.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:45.35,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you'd really go that far?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:47.95,0:03:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess this is farewell.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.26,0:03:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.99,0:03:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back on it, it's been such a short...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a short...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other since middle school, so three years.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, three years!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:03.35,0:04:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us met with a bang and brought our relationship to fruition...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No we didn't.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sup, boss?  Married couple stand-up comedy again?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't be so cold.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be having it tough too, Tanamachi.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0\fscx140} {\r}the one who has it tough!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:17.92,0:04:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Umehara-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do this because I like it.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:23.42,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How brave.  I could cry!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:25.78,0:04:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you can call me the bravest and prettiest girl in town.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.32,0:04:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Umehara-kun.  Maybe you'll know about it.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been hearing about it at my part-time job.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been to the newly-finished Port Tower?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanamachi, that's a painful question you're asking.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could go to that date spot alone!
Dialogue: 3,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have an aquarium and viewing platform there.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it sound fun?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:51.33,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about we all go together?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?  You mean, all three of us?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a place I'd rather go to for a date,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess I'll have to give up on that.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:03.63,0:05:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I could just look at it as checking the place out.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:06.89,0:05:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when should we go?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.39,0:05:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place sounds boring.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, boss?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only gonna be couples there anyway.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just gonna feel left out if we go.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know that for sure unless you go!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.55,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure there'll be families there.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, darling.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not family!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:32.86,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umehara-kun and Tanamachi-san, class is about to start,
Dialogue: 3,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so could you please take your seats?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, she's so strict.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:45.79,0:05:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayatsuji-san has to fulfill her role as the class rep.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, who's side are you on?!
Dialogue: 3,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, are you okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:00.50,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Pan...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:04.06,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dodged my right hook pretty well.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:08.59,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panties...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi, you're awake?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:26.87,0:06:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I in the infirmary?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:36.61,0:06:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fell over and hit your head and stomach.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  You brought me all the way here then, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, be thankful!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!  You're the one who hit me!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you knew.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you didn't have to hit me that hard.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.97,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped right before I hit you!
Dialogue: 3,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just happened to get hit.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say that you stopped then!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:14.35,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you've been with me the whole time?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get mad at you if you make that face.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did hit me, but... well...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to... see yours, Kaoru...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:40.65,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's how it is, so let's call it even.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were worried for me, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:52.24,0:07:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There haven't been many times when you've worried about me.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really think so...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it's still rare for you to do that.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It brought back memories.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:06.29,0:08:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of what?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:07.41,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were in middle school, we\Nskipped class in the infirmary just like this.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.92,0:08:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:13.67,0:08:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the one skipping class back then, and I'm not now.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about little details like that!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, you haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:23.06,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been unpredictable since middle school.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even earned yourself the nickname "Warhead of Kibitou".
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.82,0:08:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to close the curtains?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.28,0:08:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, take care!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I don't want you telling me that!
Dialogue: 3,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you something important.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:54.92,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:55.51,0:08:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the flower beds at the\Nback of the campus after school.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.38,0:09:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:08.35,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she go out of her way to tell me to go to a deserted place after school?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru's gonna confess to me?!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no way.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:30.96,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Sucks for you that I'm the "Warhead of Kibitou"!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:34.63,0:09:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she wouldn't need me to go to the back of the campus for that.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Which means...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaoru!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been a buddy of mine since middle school!
Dialogue: 3,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that to happen now...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:02.29,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was really worried for me just then...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}Could it be...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:11.31,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, dear.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you have dinner?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take a bath?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, could you keep it down?
Dialogue: 3,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's asleep.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an infirmary, you know.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 3,0:10:45.66,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inou Tadataka became known for his very\Naccurate map of Japan during the Edo period.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know how he made it?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rihoko!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Junichi!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.55,0:11:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.  I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.55,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi, your face is all red.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Uh... really?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:22.89,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... you don't.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:28.45,0:11:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... some graduated members of the\NTea Club are coming today, so my seniors...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.57,0:11:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!  I forgot what I came here to do!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:41.01,0:11:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:41.78,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trip, Rihoko!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:47.01,0:11:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll be okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I gotta worry about myself first.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:53.18,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Once I go around that corner...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around that corner...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.44,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually like...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:14.96,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Junichi?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Tanaka-san here?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:24.10,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to hear what Keiko has to say and give your opinion.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:30.36,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I chose you to represent all the boys in this school.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:36.04,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:39.41,0:12:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to apologize to this moron about.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you say I represent the boys in this school, then you call me a moron.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one am I?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:49.46,0:12:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.  You also have it tough, Tachibana-kun.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this mutual understanding between you two?!
Dialogue: 3,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, hurry up and hit the main subject!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:02.81,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I confessed to a guy in our class.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.68,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you wanted to talk about.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just hear her out.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:13.57,0:13:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:14.48,0:13:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He then told me to wait for his answer,
Dialogue: 3,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I waited for a while...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For how long?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably around a month.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a month?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:26.95,0:13:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 3,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many girls like you, Keiko.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A typical person wouldn't wait that long.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:34.92,0:13:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, when he finally asked for her, {\i1}that{\i0\fscx140} {\r}happened.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:40.16,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what do you think he said to Keiko?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "let me kiss you".
Dialogue: 3,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're making fun of someone, you shouldn't go that far!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:53.24,0:13:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't give her an answer and\Nleaves her alone, then he asks for a {\i1}kiss{\i0\fscx40} {\r}?!
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.67,0:13:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So Tanaka-san, what did you do?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kiss him?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:03.30,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I turned him down then, but if he asks me again...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so we're just thinking about what to do.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for asking you for weird advice.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, as the representative of the boys in this school,
Dialogue: 3,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hurry up and give us your opinion.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about my opinion...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.72,0:14:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I predict that he'll end up making Keiko cry.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:29.15,0:14:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, you didn't have to be so blunt.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My prediction doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:33.27,0:14:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's hear what you think!
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you write him a letter?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.49,0:14:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty lame.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there an easier way to solve this?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:47.56,0:14:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an easier way, you\Nwouldn't need me in the first place.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:55.08,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what are we gonna write in the letter?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.63,0:15:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something along the lines of,\N"I'm still waiting for a proper reply"?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:05.39,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you already confessed to him before,
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should take a more indirect approach instead of being persistent.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:11.55,0:15:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might ask you to kiss him again if you meet him directly, and we don't want that.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keiko, well?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's try that.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana-kun, thanks.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.21,0:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy Tanaka-san was talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not something I can just tell anyone about.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope things work out for Tanaka-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to do what it takes for that to happen too.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo things.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it all so perfect, it won't get any better.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:53.36,0:15:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  Every time you say "perfect", it's always something destructive.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "really"?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:00.91,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I have work today!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still working at that family restaurant by the train station?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:06.61,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.  We're doing a Winter Flavors fair right now.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter Flavors fair?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:13.28,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  We're putting gratin in crab shells and stuff.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, that sounds delicious.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.46,0:16:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wobbles and it's slippery.  Carrying it around is tough!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the "Crab From The North Gratin",
Dialogue: 3,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the "Full Enogi Mushroom Japanese-style Pasta".
Dialogue: 3,0:16:27.59,0:16:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have names with really lame puns.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty lame, yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:31.88,0:16:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Understood!  You want a 'Crab From The North Gratin', is that right?"
Dialogue: 3,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating the order is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess that is kinda weird.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I look for another part-time job?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:46.35,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you tried looking for a job that isn't in a family restaurant?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, lots of them.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An assistant at an attraction in a theme park, for example.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds kinda fun.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:56.84,0:16:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the competition seems fierce...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'd make it for sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:10.04,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's fun about a job?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get money.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, that's half-true.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:21.95,0:17:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's just me and my mom at home.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:26.48,0:17:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why my mom and I\Npromised each other we'd work hard.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:32.32,0:17:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame Ai-chan couldn't come.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we could do about it.  She has club activities.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I'll eat today?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll have ice cream with it!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  It's so cold though.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miya-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother's right there.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's your brother, Miya-chan...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:56.98,0:17:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 3,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your brother... are you sure?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:00.71,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We see each other at home all the time anyway.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:04.72,0:18:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I think I'll have salmon and wieners with it!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:10.14,0:18:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I might be in it for the money,
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the work itself is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:19.49,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me happy when customers show me their appreciation.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:26.05,0:18:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably give it a try too.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:28.66,0:18:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, with an apron over your uniform... it'll probably look good on you!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be in an apron?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:33.93,0:18:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you should come as a customer first.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some freebies...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't?!
Dialogue: 3,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm headed this way.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.35,0:18:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you told me to come to the flower beds today,
Dialogue: 3,0:18:57.16,0:19:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were gonna confess to me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way that would happen.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm getting the wrong idea, I shouldn't go too far.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:07.62,0:19:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your punch made me a little crazy, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:11.88,0:19:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, it's partly your fault too.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.37,0:19:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that'd happen!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.42,0:19:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I have to get to my job...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be late, late!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I said I got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to hit me.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uniform, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.  There's no way!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:49.81,0:19:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to work hard!
Dialogue: 3,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.  I decided to come right away.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I already say you won't be getting any freebies?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.  Something cheap.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the cheapest item.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about coffee?  Refills are free.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't think I can pay for anything pricier.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a coward.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just go all out and order a steak or something.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:20.14,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the "Crab From The North Gratin" from our Winter Flavors fair menu?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that hard to carry item?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:34.52,0:20:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where do you think you're looking?!
Dialogue: 3,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'm not...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I definitely wasn't looking in a perverted way...
Dialogue: 3,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all for you today?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:46.83,0:20:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like some more coffee, please.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:55.30,0:20:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:07.29,0:21:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... what's happening?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:30.44,0:21:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me I...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... like...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:35.04,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning too, when I punched him...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:37.19,0:21:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayatsuji-san has to live up to her role as the class rep.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:41.33,0:21:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he said it like he was protecting Ayatsuji-san.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:45.04,0:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:46.41,0:21:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,400)}I thought you were gonna confess to me, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:50.47,0:21:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart won't stop thumping because he said that...
Dialogue: 3,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your coffee.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:01.22,0:22:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:02.51,0:22:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:07.77,0:22:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Kaoru?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:09.96,0:22:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to tease her one more time before heading back.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:50.88,0:23:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode preview.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  What are you staring at with that huge grin on your face?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:54.60,0:23:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morishima-senpai?!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.64,0:23:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.  What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:57.77,0:24:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say I was captivated by the pristine sight of a devoted girl working hard at her part-time job.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:03.65,0:24:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you could say that I looked without thinking...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:05.21,0:24:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't help it, being a guy...
Dialogue: 3,0:24:07.32,0:24:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, so you were captivated by her thighs!
Dialogue: 3,0:24:12.03,0:24:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "Hesitation".
Dialogue: 3,0:24:13.97,0:24:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:14.76,0:24:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the girl with such sexy thighs?
Dialogue: 3,0:24:17.26,0:24:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Senpai?
